name: NEBUXEL - TEZ
description:
This piece is in honour of Tezos maximalists, and represents Gammatrace’s deep-rooted support to the digital underground artistic movement along with the pursuit of innovation and sustainability, recurring themes throughout his works.

While gazing at this piece, let yourself be transported by a connection you had taken for missing, but that is back, stronger than ever.

Within this collection, the key protagonists, the “nebuxels”, are the emissaries of this deep quest and expressive research for a deeper connection.

As a matter of fact, each nebuxel can be interpreted as the personification of one of the core elements of the metaverse: space, memory, connections, computation and decentralization…It’s just a matter of connecting the dots.

#NEBUXEL002
